2.heading: Norm.
2.title: "Headaches" p. 69-91 in Brain Songs
2.author: Uli Oesterle (Antwerpen : Bries, 2000).
notes: Summary: Norm lives alone, and is visited by an imp-like delusion named Johnathan Irrwisch. After awhile the delusion gets annoying, so Norm calls the psychiatric ward. The doctors come to take the delusion away, and quiet it by drilling a hole in its skull and inducing brain death. A year later Norm is having bad headaches, and Johnathan Irrwisch returns with a whole crowd of other delusions.
